{
  "stem": "3022.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "There wasn't one Jew that was allowed to work for that-- for that company.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "For Jews to-- to pursue a trade was made very difficult.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "You-- you know, in Poland, probably as other places in Europe, they used to have market days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "So the Jews were not allowed to purchase anything till about 10 o'clock till the Poles, the non-Jews, had an opportunity to buy whatever they wanted.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "After that-- you know, after they satisfied their needs, that's when the Jews were allowed to make purchases.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before-- before 1918, many of the tobacco kiosks were-- were in the hand of Jewish merchants.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was taken away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anything that was run by the government, which was controlled by the government, such as-- it was a government cartel-- such as sugar, alcohol, matches, salt.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Any of these items were not allowed to be traded by Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even-- I mean, in the wholesale trading, they were-- they were restricted from-- from doing their business.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were restricted from-- from export and import business, although some did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it took a great deal of ingenuity and great deal of bribery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, you know, there were famous stories that circulate about the Jew is making the bill of lading.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He's shipping pigs to-- to-- to Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he's making out the bill of lading.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He puts down Polish grapes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the other man asks him, why are you putting grapes?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You're shipping pigs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He says, you don't want me to put down Polish pigs and go to a camp, and go to jail.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because that-- that-- that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
